Property described in section 511(a) of the Comprehensive Drug Abuse Prevention and Control Act of 1970 (
21 U.S.C. 881(a)
) that is used or intended for use to commit, or to facilitate the commission of, an offense under section 70503 or 70508 of this title may be seized and forfeited in the same manner that similar property may be seized and forfeited under section 511 of that Act (
21 U.S.C. 881
).

